e":"2020-05-26T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a99128ea9c680436e7f756441dce9150b5e0660e","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"伙記 ?"},{"pid":"89bdb94758b7418f455c5a26edadda88e8939ad3","tid":2036141,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99128ea9c680436e7f756441dce9150b5e0660e","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"伙記 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係白狗? 定係分化狗"},{"pid":"93549a6c5c433ed192d31c203c05e1ef68dd91de","tid":2036141,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:01:29.000Z","msg":"有消息指國安會在遊行期間投放武漢病毒<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2034499\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2034499</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8f1a71172c2c98f87de584c1422fc969b36ea6e5","tid":2036141,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99128ea9c680436e7f756441dce9150b5e0660e","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"伙記 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:01:44.000Z","msg":"屌！copy tg 咋！"},{"pid":"c79b450ec8fb82212677688ed57b85bf51addaa9","tid":2036141,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99128ea9c680436e7f756441dce9150b5e0660e","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"伙記 ?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:02:07.000Z","msg":"成熟啲睇內容啦屌"},{"pid":"b5db64cdb0ac02fad038d3bf10fcd309a9c7058d","tid":2036141,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:04:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40544a0bb022ef7dbdc44917e623d0fe5846c322","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89bdb94758b7418f455c5a26edadda88e8939ad3","tid":2036141,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99128ea9c680436e7f756441dce9150b5e0660e","tid":2036141,"uid":324984,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T09:59:23.000Z","msg":"伙記 ?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係白狗? 定係分化狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:06:50.000Z","msg":"同埋大家打從心底... <br />\n<br />\n文章近尾的部分有伙記一詞。<br />\n<br />\n不是狗，是徹頭徹尾的深黃絲。"},{"pid":"422a960d9098a31aaf5c76a0fd0234ea1fb1b8bd","tid":2036141,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d691d3c5883e68e0951ea830b0773d9a333130e7","tid":2036141,"uid":334720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:15:17.000Z","msg":"幾時先會有奶共議員既地址整合? 等民主派多票壓制<br />\n<br />\n目的唔係阻人開會咩?<br />\n。明知都唔會夠人<br />\n。明知一定重防過上年612<br />\n。明知一定呢幾日已經運緊野去政總中聯辦<br />\n<br />\n點樣先開得成會? 無人/唔夠票既話開條撚呀?<br />\n記唔記得李慧鯨點做主席呀? <br />\n。趕撚哂民主派議員走<br />\n。奶共派40票投哂佢<br />\n<br />\n咁點解大費周章 又黎明 又堵路 又圍立法會 etc 呢d咁高危既地方<br />\n去敵方大本營守唔係本末倒置咩?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">哂時間諗塞邊條路點樣塞, 你不如爆D奶共議員既出入地點出黎 <br />\n唔撚比佢到會場仲好啦</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你地實話咩 人地可以住酒店/早一日到/住其他地方<br />\n屌你啦, 40個都圍唔到10個8個咩? 等民主派多票<br />\n咁人地立法會第2日可以再開或者改地點添</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2014/09/17/phpMrEs1u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2014%2F09%2F17%2FphpMrEs1u.jpg&h=06306a39&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"05c3a01a14398170f924db8cedea049d9896f5b8","tid":2036141,"uid":202003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:15:22.000Z","msg":"推"}],"pinned":{"pid":"f4e7465bb6fa5ee56f7ba53fb482993b68d4fa33","tid":2036141,"uid":353621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T10:21:03.000Z","msg":"手足 文中&rdquo;伙記&rdquo;一詞係on9 <br />\n但係係tg copy過黎！<br />\n覺得內容值得參考！<br />\n自膠無改佢做狗/死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係自己分析下睇下內容<br />\n唔好執著字眼"}}